menu "Van Monitor"

config VAN_MONITOR_DISPLAY_ENABLED
    bool "Enable display (ST7789T3 + CST816D touch)"
    default y
    help
        Enable the physical display and touch controller stack.
        Set to n to skip all display and touch initialisation — useful when
        developing without the target hardware connected. The web interface,
        API routes, water level sensor, and activity management all remain
        fully functional.

endmenu
